fullplot: Juanito is an actor who went to New York to succeed. Years have passed, has not achieved the success they expected, and now life working on what can be gained. One day arrives to visit his cousin, apparently a winner that has 'everything one expects to have'. However, the coexistence of both will discover the reality behind each of them.
